OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FLib Dem MP Anna Sabine asks the PM to
OL,8,Fconsider the impact of tax rises on
OL,9,Fhospices
OL,11,FHospice charity Dorothy House faces
OL,12,Fextra costs of #422,000 as a result of
OL,13,Fthe government's planned hikes to
OL,14,Femployer National Insurance
OL,15,Fcontributions, a West Country MP has
OL,16,Fsaid.
