OL,3,CHospice facing hundreds of thousands
OL,4,Cin extra costs due to tax hikes, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FThe tax rise, which was introduced in
OL,8,FOctober's Budget, will come into
OL,9,Feffect in April and will see the rate
OL,10,Fof NICs paid by employers increase
OL,11,Ffrom 13.8% to 15%.
OL,13,FThe threshold at which employers start
OL,14,Fpaying it will also decrease from
OL,15,F#9,100 to #5,000 a year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
