OL,3,CHospice facing hundreds of thousands
OL,4,Cin extra costs due to tax hikes, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FAnna Sabine, Frome and East Somerset's
OL,8,FLiberal Democrat MP, asked the Prime
OL,9,FMinister on Wednesday if he will
OL,10,Fconsider making hospices exempt from
OL,11,Fthe extra financial burden, or meet
OL,12,Fwith her to come up with a solution.
OL,14,F"I recognise the pressures that
OL,15,Fhospices are facing", Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fresponded, adding that his government
OL,17,Fhas promised an extra #100million for
OL,18,Fhospices and an additional #26million
OL,19,Ffor children and young peoples'
OL,20,Fhospices.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
