OL,3,CHospice facing hundreds of thousands
OL,4,Cin extra costs due to tax hikes, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FBut, he added, the government had to
OL,8,Fmake the "difficult, but right"
OL,9,Fdecision to announce tax rises in the
OL,10,FBudget for spending on public services.
OL,12,FNext year, Dorothy House will
OL,13,Fcelebrate its 50th year of service,
OL,14,Fwith care settings based in Bath and
OL,15,FNorth East Somerset, Frome and East
OL,16,FSomerset, and Wiltshire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
