OL,3,CHospice facing hundreds of thousands
OL,4,Cin extra costs due to tax hikes, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats have been
OL,8,Fspeaking out against the rise in
OL,9,Femployer NICs since the chancellor's
OL,10,FBudget last October, with a particular
OL,11,Ffocus on the possible impact on
OL,12,Fhospice care.
OL,14,FHospices generally get around a third
OL,15,Fof their funding from central
OL,16,Fgovernment, with the rest being raised
OL,17,Fby the hospices themselves.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
