OL,3,CHospice facing hundreds of thousands
OL,4,Cin extra costs due to tax hikes, says
OL,5,CMP
OL,7,FOver the past three years, the cost of
OL,8,Frunning Dorothy House has risen from
OL,9,F#46,000 a day to #52,000, while the
OL,10,Fnumber of people depending on
OL,11,Fspecialist end of life care is
OL,12,Fconsistently rising and the charity
OL,13,Fsays it is in urgent need of financial
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FMs Sabine, who was elected Frome and
OL,17,FEast Somerset's MP in 2024, said in
OL,18,Fthe House of Commons that her good
OL,19,Ffriend Lisa was cared for by the
OL,20,F"amazing" Dorothy House Hospice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
